          <a href="/ideas/storyarc/">storyarc</a>
          <a href="/ideas/mosarch/">mosarch</a>
          <a href="/ideas/aossc/">aossc</a>
        </div>
        <p>Part of the <a href="/staging/">mosaigoio</a> family · 🧊 draft subproject · <strong class="text-error">never executes trades</strong></p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
